# DarkChaos-255 private server (WoW 3.3.5a - Level 255 progression)
#
# Systems included:
#   1.  AoE Loot System - Collect loot from multiple corpses + DC Extensions
#   2.  Hotspots System - Random XP bonus zones across the world
#   3.  Hinterland Battleground - Custom 25v25 PvP battleground with affixes
#   4.  Mythic+ Dungeon System - Scaled dungeons, keystones & spectating
#   4B. Group Finder System - M+ Finder, Raid Finder, Scheduled Events
#   5.  Prestige System - Reset level 255 players with permanent bonuses
#   6.  Challenge Modes System - Hardcore and specialized challenge modes
#   7.  Dungeon Quest NPC System - Daily/Weekly dungeon quests
#   8.  Item Upgrade System - Progressive gear upgrade with currency
#   9.  Unified Seasonal System - Season management for all systems
#   10. AzerothCore Module Configurations - Various gameplay modules
#   11. Map Extension System - GPS tracking for custom zones
#   12. Phased Dueling System - Isolated phase duels with stat tracking
#   13. Addon Communication Protocol - DC addon client/server messaging
#   14. Unified Leaderboard System - Cross-system leaderboard aggregation
#   15. Custom Login System - First-login rewards, BoA items, DC integrations
#   16. DC-Welcome Addon System - First-start experience, FAQ, milestones
#   17. Cross-System Integration - EventBus, SessionContext, unified rewards
